  <brief_title>Study of Pimecrolimus Treatment for Atopic Dermatitis of African American Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 3-Week, Single-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Within-Patient, Randomized Study of Pimecrolimus Treatment for Atopic Dermatitis of African American Children</official_title>
